Package: inequantiles
Title: Quantile-Based Inequality Measures for Survey Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Silvia", "Scarpa", , "silvia.scarpa@unimore.it", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4003-1621"))
Description: Provides functions for estimating quantiles and quantile-based inequality indicators,
    such as the quantile ratio index, quintile share ratio, Palma index, and ratios of quantiles,
    from complex sampling data. Estimators of the influence function and
    the sampling variance via rescaled bootstrap are also provided.
